{"type": "article", "id": 13836, "title": "“Align Line”桌面收纳用品", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-21T08:09:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000243YI0gkXQdxL2lZf1V.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tKairi Eguchi 是一位来自日本的设计师，他推出了一套叫做 “Align Line” 的桌面收纳用品，像产品的名字一样，产品的设计横平竖直，他试图用简单的线条维护桌面的规则和秩序，让桌面同样整洁和简单。这个系列包括文件架，名片架，笔架，收纳盒以及一个倾斜的平面盘，颜色上采用黑白配色，同样简洁有力。<a href=\"http://kairi-eguchi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141518sQdKnjbpH2hOZvNc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141518Jv1Zmod8BnHNqlR7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141519Apar3xXcisz4kRBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141520hU96dILgkAYqjSJZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141520xLW2v7IrThMKlAYR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}